<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Brands we service</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three platforms cover the LA chain pizza market.</h2>

    <p><strong>Lincoln Impinger</strong> (Welbilt brand): 1132 standard, 1100 series mid-size, Express 2501 quick-service. The dominant chain pizza conveyor brand, including Pizza Hut and Domino's installs. Pioneered air-impingement cooking technology. See <a href="/brands/lincoln-pizza-oven-repair/">Lincoln Impinger pizza oven repair</a>.</p>

