<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Air-impingement diagnostic expertise.</strong> Lincoln Impinger finger geometry is different from blower-style or radiant-heat designs. We know which fingers fail first and why.</li>
      <li><strong>Conveyor system as a unit.</strong> Year 8+ chain operations, we replace belt plus motor plus drive sprocket as related components rather than chasing one part at a time.</li>
      <li><strong>Chain operation coordination.</strong> Corporate-authorized service network access for chain locations requiring specific certifications.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable.</li>
